snippet.title: Citizen Conflict - BATTLE ROYALE TRAILER
snippet.description:
CITIZEN CONFLICT BATTLE ROYALE MODE WILL TAKE OVER SOON

What you see is what you’ll play. Along with our TOKEN LISTING, let us drop a 'lil tease. Citizen Conflict is gearing up for the most significant release to date, boasting a whole new gaming dimension unlocked with Battle Royale hilarity. Take a peek into the most heated game mode this hot-wired esports shooter will deliver in no time. Guns out, Citizens - have your squad ready!
